      "text": "LizNoirの神崎莉央です\n今回は初めての出演で、とても楽しみにしてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m Rio Kanzaki from LizNoir.\nIt’s our first appearance on this program‚ and I was really looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.4133400284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_03-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "この番組は、私が子供の頃から見ていて……\n歌手なら誰もが、一度は憧れる番組です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been watching this program since I was a child…\nIt’s a program that every singer dreams of appearing on at least once.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.7800066951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_03-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "最高のメンバーとスタッフに恵まれて\nやっと私達もこのステージに立つことが出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to our amazing members and staff‚\nwe were finally able to stand on this stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_03-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "私が憧れた沢山のアイドル、アーティストが立った\nこのステージに相応しいパフォーマンスを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To make this performance worthy of this stage‚\nwhere countless idols and artists that I admire have stood…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.4466733618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_03-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "心を込めて……\n歌を纏って咲き誇れ！　LizNoir！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With all my heart…\nBloom‚ adorned with song! LizNoir!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.8800199194,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5399.975586199986,
