      "text": "やっぱり莉央さんは、アイドルが好きなんですよ\nだから、戻るべくして戻ったんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You really do love idols‚ Rio-san.\nThat’s why you couldn’t help but come back‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 228.5999947865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_03-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。元々は実家の喫茶店を守るために\n始めた仕事に過ぎなかったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true. It was just a job I started\nto protect my family’s cafe‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.5984094305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
