      "text": "……いつの間にか、青春全部を捧げてここにいるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…but before I knew it‚ I’ve devoted my entire youth to this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.2317895572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
