      "text": "……こうして改めて見ると\n私、随分恥ずかしいことを言ってるわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Now that I’m watching it again‚\nI said some pretty embarrassing things…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.1317498846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
