      "text": "ありがとうございます\nでは、最後にひと言メッセージをお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.\nSo‚ could you give us a message to wrap things up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.6666614532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
