      "text": "これ以上話すこと、ないわよ？\nファンへのメッセージも話したし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is there anything else I need to say?\nI’ve already given a message to the fans…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.4161203705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
